<%# Help page for next month setup %>
<div class="paper-background">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="dot-grid-overlay">
      
      <%# Back button %>
      <div class="settings-link-container">
        <%= link_to "<", settings_path, class: "settings-link" %>
      </div>
      
      <%# Header %>
      <header class="month-header">
        <h1>Next Month Setup Help</h1>
      </header>
      
      <%# Help Content %>
      <div class="help-content">
        
        <section class="help-section">
          <h2 class="help-section-title">Copy current habits</h2>
          <div class="help-text">
            <p>• Copies all your active habits from this month to next month</p>
            <p>• Keeps the same habit names and order</p>
            <p>• Takes you directly to next month's habit tracker</p>
            <p>• Perfect for maintaining consistent routines month-to-month</p>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="help-section">
          <h2 class="help-section-title">Start fresh</h2>
          <div class="help-text">
            <p>• Begin next month without any existing habits</p>
            <p>• Takes you to a clean habit creation page</p>
            <p>• Add only the habits you want for the new month</p>
            <p>• Ideal for seasonal changes or new routines</p>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="help-section">
          <h2 class="help-section-title">When to set up next month</h2>
          <div class="help-text">
            <p>• Best to set up near the end of the current month</p>
            <p>• You can set up next month at any time</p>
            <p>• Once set up, you can always modify habits later</p>
            <p>• The tracker will be ready when the new month begins</p>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="help-section">
          <h2 class="help-section-title">Navigation after setup</h2>
          <div class="help-text">
            <p>• After copying habits, use the settings (⚙) button to return to settings</p>
            <p>• Use the back (<) button to return to the current month</p>
            <p>• You can always jump between months using the navigation</p>
            <p>• Settings are available from any month's view</p>
          </div>
        </section>
        
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</div>